memberOrga:
In general, NELFA is a network of LGBTIQ* and rainbow families organisations. At the moment, we only count two individual members who joined the network as natural persons. But our member organisations themselves represent more than 20.000 people in Europe. &#xd;
&#xd;
Currently, NELFA has 38 (31 full and 7 supporting) member organisations, representing 31 European countries. See more details here: http://nelfa.org/who-we-are/members/. &#xd;
&#xd;
The mentioned countries in the Western Balkans (plus Turkey) are mainly represented in NELFA via the membership of ERA, the LGBTI Equal Rights Association for Western Balkans and Turkey, seated in Serbia.
